{
  "stem": "3382.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought that I'd rather-- and finally, the only thing I can do is to, to play [INAUDIBLE], you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I swore-- you know, I can't repeat it here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know, in Polish or in Russian, it's called a three-- a three-story swearing, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- so he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, he goes, no, I didn't think-- I didn't mean anything, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was just-- it was just, you know, it occurred to me that you look this way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But no, he says.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, when he said so, I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I started to think that I have to get out from this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know for how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We'll see what happens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Sometimes-- in September '43, the 2nd or the 3rd, I went to sleep over with my wife, you know, to the village Rulewicze because I want to know-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I brought-- I brought milk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I brought butter, you know, other things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And suddenly at night, I was awakened up by shooting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I looked up, and I saw tracers, you know, right in the direction of Zapole.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- early in the morning, I ran and found a tremendous [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That policemen ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "German soldiers were, was killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this means that they simply murdered the whole village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
